welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Flemington, Australia! Get ready to experience the charming city known for its vibrant culture, delicious food, and rich history. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Flemington has to offer during your stay."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Sydney Bankstown Airport serves domestic flights.

terminals.name: International Terminal
terminals.description: The international terminal at Sydney Bankstown Airport serves flights to and from other countries.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Terminal 1
terminals.description: The largest terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving international flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 2
terminals.description: The main domestic terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving both Qantas and Jetstar flights.

terminals.name: Terminal 3
terminals.description: A smaller domestic terminal at Sydney Kingsford Smith Airport, serving Virgin Australia and Regional Express (Rex) flights.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport, with a 3-hour time limit per session.
